{
  "_comment": "Flux de pages du BBS Oric. Modifiable a chaud. Une page a un titre, du texte (lines) et/ou des choix (entries). Avec entries = ecran interactif, sinon ecran de contenu. Une entree navigue (target: page ou __quit__/__back__/__home__) OU lance un applet (applet + next). Une page peut aussi porter un form (action login/register, fields key/label/secret, next, fail, retries) = ecran de saisie declaratif. Applets: login, register, guest, download, upload, who (qui est en ligne), chat (salon temps reel), wall (mur de messages persiste, flag serveur -wall), forum (fils de discussion paginee, flag serveur -forum), pm (messagerie privee entre membres, flag serveur -pm ; reserve aux comptes identifies). Une page peut porter un datawindow (grille de donnees, source dans sources_donnees) rendue par l'applet datawindow ; flag serveur -data requis. Couleurs ink: black red green yellow blue magenta cyan white.",
  "start": "accueil",
  "sources_donnees": {
    "annuaire": {
      "table": "annuaire",
      "tri_defaut": "nom ASC",
      "lignes_par_page": 15,
      "colonnes": {
        "id":      { "type": "INTEGER", "libelle": "ID",      "cle_primaire": true, "auto_increment": true },
        "nom":     { "type": "TEXT",    "libelle": "Nom",     "requis": true, "longueur_max": 17 },
        "adresse": { "type": "TEXT",    "libelle": "Adresse", "longueur_max": 24 }
      },
      "donnees": [
        { "nom": "BBS Oric (prod)", "adresse": "pavi.3617.fr:6502" },
        { "nom": "BBS Oric TLS",    "adresse": "pavi.3617.fr:6992" },
        { "nom": "ParticlesBBS",    "adresse": "particlesbbs.dyndns.org:6400" },
        { "nom": "Altair",          "adresse": "altair.virtualaltair.com:4667" },
        { "nom": "Heatwave",        "adresse": "heatwave.ddns.net:9640" },
        { "nom": "IDreamIn8Bits",   "adresse": "bbs.idreamtin8bits.com:6500" }
      ]
    }
  },
  "pages": {
    "accueil": {
      "title": "BIENVENUE",
      "entries": [
        {
          "key": "1",
          "label": "Se connecter",
          "target": "login"
        },
        {
          "key": "2",
          "label": "Creer un compte",
          "target": "register"
        },
        {
          "key": "3",
          "label": "Entrer en invite",
          "applet": "guest",
          "next": "main"
        },
        {
          "key": "Q",
          "label": "Quitter",
          "target": "__quit__"
        }
      ]
    },
    "login": {
      "title": "CONNEXION",
      "form": {
        "action": "login",
        "next": "main",
        "fail": "echec",
        "fields": [
          {
            "key": "login",
            "label": "Pseudo"
          },
          {
            "key": "password",
            "label": "Mot de passe",
            "secret": true
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "register": {
      "title": "CREATION DE COMPTE",
      "form": {
        "action": "register",
        "next": "main",
        "fail": "echec",
        "fields": [
          {
            "key": "login",
            "label": "Pseudo desire"
          },
          {
            "key": "password",
            "label": "Mot de passe",
            "secret": true
          },
          {
            "key": "confirm",
            "label": "Confirmer",
            "secret": true
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "echec": {
      "title": "ECHEC",
